630
00:33:19,832 --> 00:33:20,833
Don't you like it?

631
00:33:25,004 --> 00:33:26,880
Walter, it's a masterpiece.

632
00:33:28,257 --> 00:33:30,342
I've never seen anything like it before.

633
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:35,305
