in all his self-pity.

637
00:33:49,319 --> 00:33:51,572
How did you ever find
that in yourself, Walter?

638
00:33:51,739 --> 00:33:53,323
Well, it wasn't easy.

639
00:33:56,243 --> 00:33:58,287
What's the matter with you?

640
00:33:58,454 --> 00:33:59,538
