you cover it up again.

656
00:34:29,318 --> 00:34:30,318
Please, huh?

657
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,360
Please!

658
00:34:36,033 --> 00:34:37,034
Thank you.

659
00:34:37,201 --> 00:34:38,243
