738
00:37:43,387 --> 00:37:45,347
Yes, that's my man.

739
00:37:45,514 --> 00:37:46,514
Yes.

740
00:37:48,600 --> 00:37:49,768
Yes, man, yes.

741
00:37:53,230 --> 00:37:53,981
Good evening, Walter.

742
00:37:54,147 --> 00:37:55,399
Good evening, Carla.

743
00:37:58,652 --> 00:38:02,739
Sylvia, didn't you see
me wave my zen stick?

744
